reviewText: My sociology teacher plays a nurse who trys to inject women with vampire sperm. In other words... Awesome. It is very low budget but lots of tits

..as it's really just twenty some minutes of a mostly naked woman talking about wanting to be in a movie.  It's more of an outline of a movie than an actual movie.  I wasn't expecting much but I must have missed the listed run time of 30 minutes.  (It's not even that long.)  Shame, even as "bad movies" go this could have been interesting...how difficult would it have been to flesh it out?  (..pardon the pun.)  As it is, it's a waste of time and money.
